## ğŸš€ Deployment Checklist

### Pre-Deployment
- [ ] All files in version control
- [ ] Environment variables documented
- [ ] Database migrations tested
- [ ] API endpoints tested (see SETUP_GUIDE.md)
- [ ] Frontend build tested (`npm run build`)
- [ ] All 9 test scenarios passed
- [ ] Error handling verified
- [ ] Performance tested

### Deployment Steps
1. Deploy backend (FastAPI to server)
2. Deploy frontend (React build to CDN/server)
3. Configure database connection
4. Set environment variables
5. Enable HTTPS
6. Configure CORS for production domain
7. Set up monitoring/logging
8. Test end-to-end workflow

### Post-Deployment
- [ ] Verify all endpoints working
- [ ] Test with sample URLs
- [ ] Monitor error logs
- [ ] Performance monitoring
- [ ] User acceptance testing

