## ğŸ”‘ Key Features by File

### Quiz Generation Flow
1. `GenerateQuizTab.jsx` - User inputs URL
2. `main.py` `/api/generate-quiz` - API endpoint
3. `scraper.py` - Extracts Wikipedia content
4. `quiz_generator.py` - LLM generates questions
5. `main.py` - Stores in database
6. `QuizDisplay.jsx` - Displays results

### History Flow
1. `HistoryTab.jsx` - Displays table
2. `main.py` `/api/history` - Fetches data
3. Click Details â†’ `main.py` `/api/quiz/{id}`
4. `QuizDisplay.jsx` - Shows full quiz
5. Click Delete â†’ `main.py` `/api/quiz/{id}` DELETE

### Quiz Taking Flow (Bonus)
1. `QuizDisplay.jsx` - User clicks "Take Quiz Mode"
2. `QuizMode.jsx` - Interactive interface
3. User answers all questions
4. Submit â†’ `QuizMode.jsx` - Calculate score
5. Results display with breakdown

---

